<%- include('partials/header', { currentPage: 'help', title: 'Guide Book - Help Center' }) %>

<style>
    body {
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fdfdfd, #f4f7ff);
    }
    .guide-card {
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        cursor: pointer;
    }
    .guide-card:hover {
        border-color: #7f97d9;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px -10px rgba(127, 151, 217, 0.2);
    }
</style>

<main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    
    <div class="mb-12">
        <nav class="flex mb-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400">
            <a href="/dashboard/siswa/help-siswa" class="hover:text-[#7f97d9]">Help Center</a>
            <span class="mx-2">/</span>
            <span class="text-slate-600">Guide Book</span>
        </nav>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-black text-slate-800 mb-3 tracking-tight">Guide Book</h1>
        <p class="text-slate-500 font-medium italic">Everything you need to know about navigating the STM JOB ecosystem.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-6">

        <div class="guide-card bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-200 rounded-[2rem] p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
            <div class="w-36 h-36 flex-shrink-0">
                <img src="/images/regis.png" alt="Registration Guide" class="w-full h-full object-contain" onerror="this.src='https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/3456/3456426.png'">
            </div>
            <div class="text-center md:text-left">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#4a6fdc] mb-2">Registration Process</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
                    Panduan lengkap cara mendaftarkan akun siswa Anda, melakukan verifikasi email, hingga aktivasi akun oleh admin sekolah agar dapat mulai memasang lowongan.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-4 flex gap-2 justify-center md:justify-start">
                    <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 rounded-full uppercase">Getting Started</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="guide-card bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-200 rounded-[2rem] p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
            <div class="w-36 h-36 flex-shrink-0">
                <img src="/images/job.png" alt="Job Vacancy Guide" class="w-full h-full object-contain" onerror="this.src='https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/3850/3850285.png'">
            </div>
            <div class="text-center md:text-left">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#4a6fdc] mb-2">Posting Job Vacancy</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
                    Pelajari cara membuat deskripsi pekerjaan yang menarik, menentukan kriteria siswa, dan cara mengelola status lowongan (Aktif/Tutup) dengan mudah.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-4 flex gap-2 justify-center md:justify-start">
                    <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-[10px] font-bold text-blue-500 rounded-full uppercase">Recruitment</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="guide-card bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-200 rounded-[2rem] p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
            <div class="w-36 h-36 flex-shrink-0">
                <img src="/images/profile.png" alt="Profile Guide" class="w-full h-full object-contain" onerror="this.src='https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/3135/3135715.png'">
            </div>
            <div class="text-center md:text-left">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#4a6fdc] mb-2">Profile Branding</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
                    Tips mengoptimalkan profil siswa Anda. Menambahkan logo berkualitas tinggi dan deskripsi visi misi untuk menarik minat talenta terbaik dari SMK Negeri 1 Cimahi.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-4 flex gap-2 justify-center md:justify-start">
                    <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-100 text-[10px] font-bold text-purple-500 rounded-full uppercase">Branding</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="guide-card bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-200 rounded-[2rem] p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
            <div class="w-36 h-36 flex-shrink-0">
                <img src="/images/user.png" alt="User Guide" class="w-full h-full object-contain" onerror="this.src='https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2232/2232688.png'">
            </div>
            <div class="text-center md:text-left">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#4a6fdc] mb-2">Applicant Management</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
                    Cara melihat daftar pelamar, meninjau CV siswa secara online, hingga mengubah status lamaran (Diterima/Ditolak) langsung melalui dashboard Anda.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-4 flex gap-2 justify-center md:justify-start">
                    <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-green-100 text-[10px] font-bold text-green-500 rounded-full uppercase">Dashboard</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>